branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series VFR consists of 5 port pilot solenoid valves with rubber seals and base mounted type manifolds, available in plug-in and non plug-in styles. Port sizes range from 1/8 to 1/2 with Rc(PT), NPTF &amp; G(PF) thread types available. Various options also available.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchCategory.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;VFR3000 series manifold (all types)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plug-in &amp; non plug-in styles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wiring types (non plug-in): grommet, grommet terminal,&lt;br&gt;Conduit terminal, DIN connector, L plug connector&lt;br&gt;M plug connector&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wiring types (plug-in): terminal block, multi-connector,&lt;br&gt;D-sub connector&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maximum stations: 11 (depending on style)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

